# Frontend — agent rules

> Canonical context is in `AGENTS.md`. Read it first.

- Stack, commands, conventions, Don'ts → `AGENTS.md`
- Design system → `design.md` (read in full before UI changes)
- Data layer → `.ai/context/data-layer.md`
- Routing → `.ai/context/routing.md`
- Charts / P&L → `.ai/context/charts-ui.md`

No business calculations in the frontend — backend computes, UI displays.
